title: Galactus Cometh
description: Phil Sheldon and Ben Urich gain front row seats to the greatest battle the world has ever witnessed: Galactus versus The Fantastic Four. Starring AnnaSophia Robb as Marcia Hardesty; Seth Barrish as Phil Sheldon; Method Man as Ben Urich; Ryan Andes as Galactus.
author: originals@stitcher.com (MARVELS)
